{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2015/06/east-star/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/thinking/","name":"折腾随想"}],"tags":[{"name":"东方之星","path":"/tag/east-star/"},{"name":"事故","path":"/tag/accident/"},{"name":"娱乐至死","path":"/tag/entertainment-to-death/"},{"name":"沉船","path":"/tag/shipwreck/"},{"name":"监利","path":"/tag/jianli/"},{"name":"长江","path":"/tag/yangtze/"}],"featured_media":{"source_url":"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/eastStarShip.jpg"},"path":"/2015/06/east-star/","date":"2015-06-03T11:10:24.000Z","excerpt":"希望这件“黑天鹅”事件，能对长江航运产生一些影响，让人们能更加安全的生活。 熬了一夜做这个东西，当我在为短片配 … ","title":"3D动画还原“东方之星”最后轨迹","content":"<p><embed src=\"http://static.video.qq.com/TPout.swf?vid=m0155qd5pgn&amp;auto=0\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\"/></p>\n<p>希望这件“黑天鹅”事件，能对长江航运产生一些影响，让人们能更加安全的生活。</p>\n<p>熬了一夜做这个东西，当我在为短片配上背景音乐的时候，想起来《娱乐至死》中那些令人担忧的观点了，不过武汉经视直播新闻中那史诗配乐，才是把沉船事故不折不扣的渲染成了一部大片。</p>\n<p>把伪善当作爱真是可怕的事。</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2015/06/east-star/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","3675143411","4019104361"]}